name: Joye Ego Review

overview: All these three models also are priced about the same at about 78 to eighty dollars. But what’s great about Joye Ego compared with the other two is, if you buy their package they include two batteries, 2 atomizers, two cones, 5 cartridges and 1 fast charger plus a 510 to 901 adapter unlike Cruel and Janty Ego, their packages only includes two batteries, two atomizers, charger and one cone
